&lt;p&gt;The Product Development Manager is responsible for managing the development and production of SanMar products. The Product Development Manager leads the development process from initial concept to commercialized product. The role works with the product and merchandising teams to drive new product development, cost savings, responsible sourcing, and customer satisfaction. The Product Development Manager supports the training and development of junior staff within the Product Development Team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What Will You Be Doing?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
