&lt;li&gt;Lead and drive the product development process from design, materials, and trim concepts into a manufacturable, top quality, and commercialized finished product; manage the product&#39;s life cycle.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop fabric, trims, and styles with suppliers; oversee color development and management, including lab dips and bulk materials.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Research emerging material, trim, and style trends by attending material and industry shows and meeting with suppliers, mills, and factories to present innovative ideas.&lt;/li&gt;
