&lt;li&gt;Understand key cost drivers affecting product development to ensure that the materials selected can be commercialized into compelling and profitable products while working closely with suppliers and internal partners to meet margin requirements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Execute seasonal development calendars to meet deadlines, costing KPI, and quality standards.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage monthly capacities and work-in-progress reports to ensure on-time delivery of products; collaborate with the planning team to balance order flows that fit with suppliers’ capabilities and capacities.&lt;/li&gt;
